01Gn 31:25 Meanwhile, Jacob had pitched his tent on the mountain, where Laban had caught up with him. Laban and his relatives encamped on that same mountain in the hill country of Gilead, too.
01Gn 31:26 Then Laban asked Jacob, "What did you do -  You deceived me, carried off my daughters like you would war captives, 
