01Gn 32:13 Jacob spent the night there. Out of everything that he had brought with him, he chose a gift for his brother Esau -  
01Gn 32:14 200 female goats, 20 male goats, 200 ewes, 20 rams, 
01Gn 32:15 30 milking camels with their young, 40 cows with ten bulls, and 20 female donkeys with ten male donkeys. 
