01Gn 50:16 So they sent this message to Joseph£º 
01Gn 50:17 "Before he died, your father left some instructions. He told us, "Tell Joseph, 'Please forgive your brothers' offenses. I beg you, forgive their sins, because they wronged you.'" So please forgive the transgression of the servants of your father's God." Joseph wept when they talk to him. 
01Gn 50:18 So his brothers went to visit, fell prostrate in his presence, and declared, "Look! We're your servants."
01Gn 50:19 "Don't be afraid," Joseph responded. "Am I sitting in God's place -  
