02Ex 24:8 Moses took the blood, sprinkled it on the people, and said, "This is the blood of the covenant which the Lord made with you based on all these words."
02Ex 24:9 Then Moses and Aaron, Nadab and Abihu and seventy of the elders of Israel went up 
02Ex 24:10 and saw the God of Israel. Under his feet was something like a pavement made of sapphire, and as clear as the sky. 
02Ex 24:11 Because God did not punish the Israelite leaders, they looked at God, yet lived to eat and drink.
