04Nm 9:21 There were times when the cloud remained from evening until morning, but when the cloud ascended in the morning, they would journey. Whether by day or by night, they would travel whenever the cloud ascended. 
04Nm 9:22 Whether for two days, a month, or for longer periods, whenever the cloud would remain above the tabernacle, the Israelites would remain in camp, not traveling. But whenever it ascended, then they would travel. 
