04Nm 31:13 Moses and Eleazar the priest and all the leaders of the community went out to meet them outside the camp.
04Nm 31:14 But Moses became livid with anger at the officers of the army, the captains of thousands, and the captains of hundreds who had returned from servicing in the battle. 
04Nm 31:15 "Did you keep all the women alive?" Moses asked them. 
04Nm 31:16 "Look! These women were the same ones who were counseled by Balaam to cause the Israelites to commit a grievous sin against the Lord at Peor. As a result, that plague infected the Lord's community. 
04Nm 31:17 You are to kill every male child and every woman who has had sexual relations with a man. 
04Nm 31:18 You are to allow the young women who haven't yet had sexual relations with a man to live for yourselves."17
