04Nm 31:21 Eleazar the priest told soldiers who had gone to battle, "This is the ordinance of the law that the Lord commanded Moses 
04Nm 31:22 concerning anything containing gold, silver, brass, iron, tin, and lead, 
04Nm 31:23 or anything that can survive a refiner's fire£º You are to pass it through fire, after which it will be clean. Then it is to be purified with the water of impurity. Everything that cannot survive a refiner's fire is to be washed in water. 
04Nm 31:24 Wash your clothes on the seventh day, after which you will be clean. Then you may enter the camp."23
04Nm 31:25 Then the Lord said to Moses, 
