04Nm 32:1 Now, the Reubenites and Gaddites happened to be joint owners of a very large herd of cattle. When they observed that Jazer and Gilead were good grazing lands for cattle, 
04Nm 32:2 the Gaddites and Reubenites approached Moses, Eleazar the priest, and the leaders of the community and said, 
04Nm 32:3 "Ataroth, Dibon, Jazer, Nimrah, Heshbon, Elealeh, Sebam, Nebo, and Beon - 
